<br>
<br>
<br>
Naggy Going Down Feb 13th 8:30pm EST .Open/invites via email<br>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>
As of Monday Feb 10th 34 people have signed up via email. we are looking to max out at 42 peeps for this raid so if you want to come to the raid please email me so i can add you to the list. Don't be turned away at the door<br>
we are especially in search of clerics (46-52), bards (46-52)and wizards (49-52 with ice comet) but there are still a few spaces available for other classes.<br>
